        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2011-12-09 17:16:48.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nLiang, it would be great to get such data in the commit comment. It will definitely be needed for upstream submission. Are you able to measure any performance increase with vanilla ext4 so that this can be submitted upstream?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 6
    },
